          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人有所不知，时才探马报到，只因我父杨波，在朝中与奸贼徐赞顶本，可恨"
        },
        {
          "character": "马芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昏王，将我父削去官职，囚禁南牢，你道恼是不恼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有此事，老爷就该点动人马，搭救我父才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅也有此意，就请夫人点动雄兵，校场伺候。本帅后面披挂。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "马芳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恼恨昏王与徐赞，"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "点兵救父报仇冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马芳下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里在二堂忙传将令，"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫一声众将官细听分明："
        }
      ],
